Output demos/review-session.gif

Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1200
Set Height 600
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 100ms
Set Shell "bash"

Hide
Type "export PATH=$PWD/target/release:$PATH" Enter
Sleep 500ms
Show

Type "# Start a review session" Sleep 500ms Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type "zen start" Sleep 500ms Enter
Sleep 2s

Space
Sleep 1500ms

Type "3"
Sleep 2s

Space
Sleep 1500ms

Type "4"
Sleep 2s

Space
Sleep 1500ms

Type "2"
Sleep 2s
